CellPac.Name: Sequel® II SMRT® Cell 8M (4/tray)
CellPac.Description: Individual 4 Pack containing 4 SMRT®Cells each containing 7.76 million ZMWs

ControlKit.Name: Sequel® II DNA Internal Control 0.9
ControlKit.Description: The Sequel Dev DNA Internal Control 1.0 contains a fixed template of 2 kb length bound to Sequel Dev Binding Kit 1.0 for use as an internal sequencing control. Reagent quantities provide spike-in controls for a minimum of 24 samples.

TemplatePrepKit.Name: SMRTbell® Template Prep Kit 1.0
TemplatePrepKit.Description: The SMRTbell® Template Prep Kit contains reagent supplies to perform SMRTbell library preparations of primer-annealed SMRTbell libraries for insert sizes ranging from 500 bp to over 20 kb.

BindingKit.Name: Sequel® II Binding Kit 0.9
BindingKit.Description: The Sequel II Binding Kit 0.9 contains reagent supplies to bind prepared DNA template libraries to the Sequel Polymerase 1.0 in preparation for sequencing on the Sequel System. The result is a DNA polymerase/template complex. Sequel Dev Binding Kit 1.0 should be used only with Sequel Dev Sequencing Kit 1.0. Reagent quantities support 24 binding reactions.

SequencingKitPlate.Name: Sequel® II Sequencing Plate 0.9 (4 rxn)
SequencingKitPlate.Description: The DNA Sequencing Kit contains a sequencing reagent plate with chemistry for single molecule real-time sequencing on the PacBio Sequel® Dev. Reagent quantities support 4 sequencing reactions to be used in conjunction with SMRT® Cell 4Pac(s). (4 Cells max/Each Row supplies reagents for 1 Sequel SMRT Cell)
